====================================================
        GENDER WELCOME BOT — PROJECT PROFILE
====================================================

PROJECT NAME   : Gender Welcome Bot
FILE           : b.py
LANGUAGE       : Python 3
TYPE           : Telegram Bot
PURPOSE        : Telegram groups mein naye members ko
                 unke gender ke hisaab se welcome karna

----------------------------------------------------
BOT KYA KARTA HAI?
----------------------------------------------------
- Jab koi naya member group join karta hai, bot
  automatically unka naam dekhkar gender detect karta
  hai (Male / Female / Neutral)
- Gender ke hisaab se alag-alag welcome message
  aur video bhejta hai
- Agar gender detect na ho (Neutral), to member
  ko buttons dikhata hai: "Ladka Hoon" / "Ladki Hoon"
- Admins DM se bhi apna group manage kar sakte hain
  (connect/disconnect feature)

----------------------------------------------------
MAIN FEATURES
----------------------------------------------------
1. Gender Detection (3-Layer System)
   - Layer 1 : Name list se exact match (MALE_NAMES / FEMALE_NAMES)
   - Layer 2 : Name ke andar substring match
   - Layer 3 : Name endings se detect (e.g. -devi, -raj)

2. Welcome Message System
   - Male, Female, Neutral — teeno ke liye alag message
   - Variables support: {name}, {username}, {mention}, {gender}

3. Welcome Video System
   - Har gender ke liye multiple videos store ho sakti hain
   - Random video select hoti hai welcome par

4. Admin Commands (DM + Group dono se)
   - Group connect/disconnect
   - Welcome message set karna
   - Video welcome set karna
   - Settings dekhna aur reset karna

5. Inline Button Callback
   - Neutral member khud apna gender choose kare
   - Sirf wahi member button press kar sakta hai

----------------------------------------------------
COMMANDS LIST
----------------------------------------------------
/start            - Bot ka intro aur help
/connect          - Group ko bot se connect karo
/disconnect       - Connection hatao
/setwelcome       - Welcome message set karo
/setvideowelcome  - Welcome video set karo
/showwelcome      - Current settings dekho
/resetwelcome     - Saari settings reset karo
/testgender       - Kisi naam ka gender test karo
/admincheck       - Apna admin status check karo

----------------------------------------------------
DATA STORAGE
----------------------------------------------------
- File    : bot_data.json (local JSON file)
- Format  : Per-group settings (messages + videos)
- Connections map: User ID → Group Chat ID

----------------------------------------------------
DEVELOPER NOTES
----------------------------------------------------
- BOT_TOKEN environment variable se liya jaata hai
- Logging enabled (INFO level)
- Unicode normalization for Hindi/Urdu names
- Fully async (python-telegram-bot v20+)

